{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Crimen Exceptum</strong> is a spell-crafting action roguelike where you collect and combine powerful spells to take on ever increasing challenges within your journey across a fantasy-medieval world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You awaken within your coffin to the murmur of mysterious cultists, for it is they who have brought you back from death. Guided by their crazed counsel and a few faint memories of a past life, you set out to explore the ravaged remnants of the world you once knew and take revenge on the wicked Necromancer who brought it to ruin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423240/extras/wand_building.gif?t=1739814024\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>COMBINE POWERFUL SPELLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapt to your situation by combining individual spells to create a massive variety of magic to use as your weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423240/extras/fight.gif?t=1739814024\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIGHT WITH NECROMANCER'S ENVOYS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your spells to engage in fast-paced combat against a range of unique enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423240/extras/explore.gif?t=1739814024\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>EXPLORE AN ENCHANTED WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enter an ever-changing world filled with magic, diverse biomes, creatures, and mystical places waiting to be explored.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepageb